README for Xfce 4.12

REQUIREMENTS

PRE-INSTALL

POST-INSTALL

PRECAUTION

  Update/install ports in the following order:

     - libxfce4util
     - libxfce4ui (new in 4.8)
     - xfconf
     - exo (new in 4.8)
     - garcon (new in 4.8)
     - libxfcegui4 (deprecated since 4.8)
     - xfce4-panel
     - thunar
     - xfce4-settings, xfce4-session, xfdesktop, xfwm4, xfwm4-themes, xfce4-appfinder, ...
    
  or use prt-get:

    prt-get update `prt-get quickdep xfce4`

NOTES

  For information about theme customization:
  https://wiki.xfce.org/howto/install_new_themes
